title: Nutrition — Cancer Rehab and Integrative Medicine
cleaned_text: BCBS, Humana, and United. Please contact our Krystle directly for rates and availability. Our Cancer Dietitian Krystle Zuniga PhD, RD, CSO, LD Dr. Krystle Zuniga has a PhD in Nutritional Sciences and completed her dietetic internship at the University of Illinois Urbana-Champaign. In partnership with Cancer Rehab and Integrative Medicine, she provides educational seminars and workshops using evidence-based nutrition to help cancer survivors develop individualized nutrition care plans that meet nutrient needs, manage side effects, and promote health and recovery.
